Package: shinySIR
Type: Package
Title: Interactive plotting for mathematical models of infectious disease spread
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-11-23
Authors@R: person("Sinead E.", "Morris", role = c("aut", "cre"),
		   email = "sinead.morris@columbia.edu",
		   comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8626-1698"))
Maintainer: Sinead E. Morris <sinead.morris@columbia.edu>
Description: This package provides interactive plotting for mathematical models of infectious disease spread. Users can choose from a variety of common built-in ODE models (such as the SIR, SIRS, and SIS models), or create their own. The package is a useful teaching tool as students can visualize how changing different parameters can impact model dynamics, with minimal knowledge of coding in R.
